    • generateUuid

      public final void generateUuid()
      Add default values for sourceId and sourceName if they are not provided before persisting this object. The default for sourceId is to generate a new UUID. The default for sourceName is to take to model name, and append a dash followed by the first 8 characters of the string representation of the UUID.
